## 4. tRPC Routers

### Root app (`server/routers.ts`)

- **system:** `systemRouter` (from `server/_core/systemRouter.ts`)
- **auth:** `me` (current user), `logout` (clear session cookie)
- **agents:** `agentsRouter` (server/routers/agents.ts) — multi-agent suggestions, LLM, RAG
- **catalog:** `catalogRouter` (server/routers/catalog.ts) — catalog management, caching, sync

Context and procedures live in `server/_core/` (trpc, context). Cookie name from `@shared/const`.

### control-panel (`src/server/api/root.ts`) — when present

- Core: `apiToken`, `user`, `payment`, `admin`, `paymentHistory`, `creditAllocation`, `airdropAdmin`
- Business: `customerList`, `emailCampaign`, `messaging`, `socialMedia`, `chat`, `stock`
- Invoicing: `invoice-numbering` (sub-router)

### dashboard (`src/server/api/root.ts`) — when present

- `apiToken`, `user`, `payment`, `airdrop`

### Procedure types (packages)

- `publicProcedure` — no auth
- `protectedProcedure` — requires session
- `adminProcedure` — `protectedProcedure` + `isAdminEmail`
- `companyProcedure` — session required, `isAdmin` forbidden

