## 12. Story Workflow Reference

Every feature follows: **Story → Code → Test → Done**

- Stories live in `docs/stories/STORY-<N>-<slug>.md`
- Tracker: `docs/stories/TRACKER.md` (next story number at top)
- Status values: 🟡 In Progress, ✅ Done, 🔴 Blocked, ⚫ Cancelled
- Tests: write alongside implementation, every AC needs a test
- Mark done: update story status, check off ACs, fill Files Changed, update TRACKER

