### Test health

- Run **`pnpm test`** (`vitest run`) at repo root; release-style gate: **`pnpm run smoke`** (`vitest run && vite build`). Client-only bundle check: **`pnpm exec vite build`**. Integration tests may use `vitest.integration.config.ts` / `pnpm test:integration` when present. Re-count tests after large changes and note in tracker if you maintain “last guardian review” lines.

